    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a pretty grim outlook lol. i mean, i hear a lot of people saying that raising the wage is actually good because it puts more money in the pockets of locals so they spend more at shops like mine. is there any real evidence that it actually helps the local economy, or is that just a nice idea?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
